a list of all trains that ply the route (including all trains that are just passing by your selected stations), listed with their start and end cities and times. click on a train number you like, and you can find the prices for all the classes of seats or berths that are available by clicking check price further down the price. the most important thing here is to get your town names right in "pinyin", the characters are never separated by a space, ie: lijiang, beijing, shanghai, shenzhen, kunming etc. by bus[edit] a sightseeing bus in shanghai travelling by public 